# Commerce Backend Standards

Trước khi code hoặc review bất kỳ thứ gì liên quan **Commerce Service**, bắt buộc tuân thủ chuẩn backend chung (`.cursor/rules/social/social-backend-standards.mdc`) **và** toàn bộ quy tắc dưới đây. Source-of-truth nghiệp vụ: `docs/business-spec/commerce-service-spec.md`.

## 1. Service Boundary

- **Own:** shop, product, inventory, cart, address, order, payment, shipment, review, `outbox_events`.
- **PostgreSQL only** cho MVP (`commerce_db`, port local **5434**). Không MongoDB trong commerce-service.
- **Không** truy cập DB Auth/Social/Admin. Chỉ lưu `user_id` / `buyer_id` / `seller_id` / `payer_id` (UUID). User/profile/role lấy từ **JWT claims** hoặc contract API/event — không cross-DB FK.
- Mỗi user tối đa **1 cart**, **1 seller shop** (MVP).
- Cart **không** reserve stock; chỉ **checkout** reserve (`stock_quantity` ↓, `reserved_quantity` ↑).

## 2. Architecture & Package

Dependency flow: `delivery → application → domain → infrastructure` (không đảo chiều).

```
src/main/java/com/twohands/commerce_service/
├── application    # UseCase, @Transactional write boundary
├── delivery       # Controller, XxxRequest/XxxResponse, mapper
├── domain         # Entity, rule, repository interface (no Spring/HTTP/Kafka)
├── infrastructure # JPA, Redis, PayOS/GHN client, outbox adapter
├── config / common / exception / security
```

**Use case naming:** `CheckoutFromCartUseCase`, `ProcessPayOSWebhookUseCase` — không `XxxService` generic.

**Forbidden (Commerce):**
- Controller → repository trực tiếp.
- Business logic trong DTO/Controller.
- Expose JPA entity ra API.
- Publish broker trong transaction trước commit (phải outbox).
- Gọi PayOS/GHN trong DB transaction dài.
- Tin giá/stock/status từ client khi checkout — **revalidate server-side**.
- Order/shipment tham chiếu mutable `user_addresses` — phải dùng `shipping_address_snapshots`.

## 3. API Contract

| Mục | Quy tắc |
|-----|---------|
| Base path (FR + api-standard) | `/commerce/api/v1/{resource}` |
| Local | `http://localhost:3003` |
| Envelope | `docs/engineering_rules/api-standard.md` — `code`, `success`, `message`, `data`, `errors`, `timestamp` |
| Error prefix | `COMMERCE-*` (vd: `COMMERCE-404`, `COMMERCE-400-VALIDATION`) — mở rộng trong `ErrorCode` theo domain |
| DELETE | Soft delete / status transition (`ARCHIVED`, `REMOVED`, `HIDDEN`) — không hard delete mặc định |
| Webhook | `POST /commerce/api/v1/payments/webhooks/payos`, `POST /commerce/api/v1/shipments/webhooks/ghn` — `permitAll`, verify signature, idempotent |

Khi implement controller, **ưu tiên path trong `docs/feature_requirements/commerce/FR_*.md`**. Nếu `SecurityConfig` lệch prefix, sửa cho khớp FR.

**Auth:** Bearer JWT mọi API protected. Buyer/Seller/Admin: validate ownership + role/permission từ JWT (admin từ Auth).

## 4. Domain State Machines (tóm tắt bắt buộc)

### Product
`DRAFT → ACTIVE → OUT_OF_STOCK`; `ACTIVE ↔ PAUSED`; `→ ARCHIVED | REMOVED` (admin remove).

### Order
`CREATED → AWAITING_PAYMENT → PROCESSING → COMPLETED`; cancel từ `CREATED`/`AWAITING_PAYMENT` (và `PROCESSING` chỉ khi policy + shipment còn `PENDING`).

### Order item
`PENDING → PROCESSING → SHIPPED → DELIVERED → COMPLETED`; cancel trước fulfillment; `FAILED`/`RETURNED` khi giao lỗi.

### Payment (1:1 order)
Methods: `COD`, `PAYOS`. Status: `PENDING → PAID | FAILED | CANCELLED | EXPIRED`.
- **PAYOS:** paid **chỉ** từ webhook hợp lệ; redirect không đánh dấu paid.
- **COD:** `cod_amount` trên shipment; paid khi buyer confirm / settlement rule.

### Shipment
Chỉ tạo khi order **`PROCESSING`** và payment đã đủ điều kiện (PayOS: `PAID`). Carrier: `GHN`, `MANUAL`, `SELF_DELIVERY`.
`PENDING → PICKING_UP → READY_TO_SHIP → SHIPPED → DELIVERED` — **DELIVERED không auto-complete order** (confirm buyer hoặc job 7 ngày).

### Review
`UNIQUE(order_item_id)`; chỉ khi `order_items.status = COMPLETED`; rating 1–5; `VISIBLE | HIDDEN`.

### Outbox
`PENDING → PROCESSING → PUBLISHED`; fail → `FAILED` → retry. Ghi cùng transaction domain change.

## 5. Inventory Invariants

```text
Checkout:     stock_quantity -= q; reserved_quantity += q
Pay success:  reserved_quantity -= q   (stock đã trừ lúc reserve)
Pay fail/exp: reserved_quantity -= q; stock_quantity += q
```

- `stock_quantity >= 0`, `reserved_quantity >= 0`.
- Checkout fail nếu `stock_quantity < quantity`.
- Cập nhật stock: optimistic/pessimistic lock — tránh oversell.
- `available_stock` (nghiệp vụ) = `stock_quantity` trong schema MVP.

## 6. Data & Schema

- Schema doc: `docs/database/commerce-schema.md`
- Migration: `Services/commerce-service/src/main/resources/db/migration/V1__init_commerce_tables.sql`
- PK UUID; money `numeric`; timestamps TZ-aware; JSON → JSONB.
- **Snapshots bắt buộc** trên `order_items` (price, SKU, name, image, attributes, shop name, `shipping_fee_allocated`) và `shipping_address_snapshots` cho shipment.
- Status history: `order_status_history`, `payment_status_history`, `shipment_status_history` khi đổi state quan trọng.
- Webhook logs: `payment_webhook_logs` (unique `provider + payos_order_code + event_type`), `ghn_webhook_logs`.

## 7. Outbox & Kafka Topics

- Không publish trực tiếp từ use case; insert `outbox_events` trong transaction.
- `event_type`: `COMMERCE_*` UPPER_SNAKE; `event_key` deterministic (vd: `order:{id}:created`).
- `source`: `commerce` | `payment` | `shipment`.
- Topic map (đã có `CommerceOutboxTopicResolver`): `commerce.order.created`, `commerce.payment.paid`, `commerce.shipment.status_changed`, … — thêm entry khi thêm `event_type` mới.
- Worker: `PublishCommerceEventsUseCase`, `RetryCommerceOutboxEventsUseCase` (schedulers tắt mặc định).

Event candidates (spec §8): `COMMERCE_ORDER_CREATED`, `COMMERCE_PAYMENT_PAID`, `COMMERCE_INVENTORY_RESERVED`, `COMMERCE_PRODUCT_PUBLISHED`, `COMMERCE_REVIEW_CREATED`, …

## 8. Media / MinIO (Object Storage)

- **MinIO shared** từ `Infrastructure/docker-compose.yml` — **không** instance MinIO riêng cho commerce-service.
- **Buckets:** `2hands-commerce-product`, `2hands-commerce-review`, `2hands-commerce-shop` (auth: `2hands-avatar` riêng).
- **DB:** chỉ URL + metadata; binary trên MinIO. Checkout: `image_snapshot` từ product media URL.
- **Upload MVP:** FE presigned → MinIO → API lưu URL (giống Auth avatar). Review: thêm multipart proxy (`FR_UploadReviewMedia`).
- **Chi tiết:** `docs/engineering_rules/commerce-object-storage.md`, `docs/business-spec/commerce-service-spec.md` § 1.1.
- **Env gợi ý:** `COMMERCE_MINIO_ENDPOINT`, `COMMERCE_MINIO_PUBLIC_URL`, `COMMERCE_MINIO_BUCKET_*` (xem `.env.example`).

## 9. External Integrations

| Provider | Bật khi | Env chính |
|----------|---------|------------|
| PayOS | `COMMERCE_PAYOS_ENABLED=true` | `COMMERCE_PAYOS_WEBHOOK_SECRET`, `COMMERCE_PAYOS_BASE_URL` (+ API credentials khi implement client) |
| GHN | `COMMERCE_GHN_ENABLED=true` | `COMMERCE_GHN_TOKEN`, `COMMERCE_GHN_WEBHOOK_SECRET`, `COMMERCE_GHN_BASE_URL` |

- Webhook: verify signature → log raw → idempotent process → update payment/shipment/order/inventory.
- Không log secret, token, signature key, full PAN.
- GHN status map (MVP): picking→`PICKING_UP`, delivering→`SHIPPED`, delivered→`DELIVERED`, failure→`FAILED`/`RETURNED`.

## 10. Background Jobs

Theo `docs/business_flow/commerce_business_flow/background-jobs-flow.md` + `uc-background-jobs.md`:

- Sync cart item (`OUT_OF_STOCK`, `INVALID_PRODUCT`) khi product/shop/stock đổi.
- Expire PayOS payment / auto-cancel unpaid order.
- Auto-complete delivered order (~7 ngày).
- Outbox publish/retry.

Job bật qua config scheduler; mặc định **false** local.

## 11. Local Development

```bash
cd Infrastructure && docker compose up -d postgres-commerce redis minio
```

Copy `Services/commerce-service/.env.example` → `.env`:

- `DB_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5434/commerce_db`
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` / `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET` (≥32 chars, **cùng auth-service** khi test JWT)
- Outbox/PayOS/GHN: để `false` / secret trống cho dev thuần CRUD

Chạy: `./gradlew bootRun` (port **3003**). Health: `/actuator/health`.

